## 3D Printing

freecad                     # https://www.freecadweb.org/
aur/luxcorerender           # https://luxcorerender.org/ (FreeCAD render)
openscad                    # https://openscad.org/
f3d                         # https://github.com/f3d-app/f3d
librecad                    # https://librecad.org/
flatpak/com.prusa3d.PrusaSlicer         # https://github.com/prusa3d/PrusaSlicer
flatpak/io.github.softfever.OrcaSlicer  # https://github.com/SoftFever/OrcaSlicer
flatpak/io.github.nokse22.Exhibit       # https://github.com/Nokse22/Exhibit

